oai_dc:dc.dc:title: Original wills, Baker, Johnetta, 1900 August 09
oai_dc:dc.dc:description: An original will of Johnetta Baker, dated July 3rd, 1900. Illustrates the first page of the document, written on stationery of the T.E. Baker & Bro. Groceries and Country Produce … Grain and Hay …, 329 Broad Street. The notation on the envelope: “prob 9-9-1900; WB 35:449; MB 5:452.” Forms part of Record Group 16, Original Wills, 1780-1925.
